            "title": "Lesson #2 - Copy",
            "id": 131703,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Les variables d'environnement doivent toujours être stockées de manière sécurisée pour protéger les informations sensibles.</p><p>Tu ne devrais jamais coder en dur tes clés API ou mots de passe ; l'exemple suivant est à des fins éducatives pour démontrer leur structure.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"environment_variables = {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"&quot;API_KEY&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\": \" /><text value=\"&quot;12345-abcde-67890-fghij-12345&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\",\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"&quot;SECRET_KEY&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\": \" /><text value=\"&quot;mysecretkey&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(environment_variables)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Don't do the above! It's dangerous to expose sensitive information directly in your code!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"{'API_KEY': '12345-abcde-67890-fghij-12345', 'SECRET_KEY': 'mysecretkey'}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Don't do the above! It's dangerous to expose sensitive information directly in your code!\" /></content></output></code></body></html>"
